narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I definitely recommend taking this course. It's fun and doesn't require too much work on your part so long as you do put in some effort at the very least.

It's a very chill class. Swapna ji is a good teacher, but since she pretty much rolls with what the class wants how much you learn in the end depends on the class you are in. Make of it what you will. Small size, around 10 people.
Great class! Definitely take it if you can. You end up becoming really good friends with everyone in the class and Swapnaji is so sweet.
It is a good way to improve Hindi.
